summary: The Enchantment from Dragonborn, Water-walking, is now unlocked!
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]T[/size]he [color=#008080][size=5]Enchantment[/size][/color] from [size=5][color=#daa520]Dragonborn[/color][/size], [b][color=#40e0d0][size=6]Water-walking[/size][/color][/b], is now [size=7][color=#00ff00]unlocked![/color][/size]
[color=#f0f8ff][size=7]----------------------------------[/size][/color]
[size=6][color=#add8e6]The enchantment, [/color][color=#00ffff]Water-walking[/color][color=#add8e6] has been unlocked and added to the armours: [/color][color=#000000]\'Daedric boots of Waterwalking\', and \'Leather boots of Waterwalking\'[/color][/size]
[color=#f0f8ff][size=7]----------------------------------[/size][/color]
[size=8][color=#ff0000]PLEASE report any bugs to me in either Private Message or in the comments section![/color][/size]
[color=#ff0000][size=6](Private Messages have higher priority)[/size][/color]
[color=#f0f8ff][size=7]----------------------------------[/size][/color]
[size=8][color=#006400]Thank you all![/color][/size]
[color=#f0f8ff][size=7]----------------------------------[/size][/color]
[size=8][color=#000000][font=lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif]~Tobias Luke Hana[/font][/color][/size]
author: Tobias Luke Hana
